ITV Tour De France 2012 Stage 14 Highlights PDTV x264 AAC

Presented by Gary Imlach, Chris Boardman and Ned Boulting. Commentary: Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen. Stage 14 highlights, Limoux to Foix. The road is never flat today as the peloton gets its first taste of the Pyrenees. Rolling roads all day culminate in two huge Category-One mountains that will ensure a small group of riders at the stage finish in Foix.
